<h2 style="color: #2C5234; margin-bottom: 20px;">New Community Survey</h2>

<p>Hello {{recipientName}},</p>

<p>A new survey has been posted by the Summit Ridge HOA board and your input is important to us!</p>

<div style="background-color: #f5f6f7; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
    <h3 style="color: #2C5234; margin-top: 0;">Survey Question:</h3>
    <p style="font-size: 16px;">{{surveyQuestion}}</p>
    
    <p style="margin-top: 15px;">
        <strong>Survey End Date:</strong> {{surveyEndDate}}
    </p>
</div>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <a href="{{surveyUrl}}" class="button" style="font-size: 16px;">
        Take Survey Now
    </a>
</div>

<p>Please complete this survey before the end date to ensure your voice is heard in our community decisions.</p>

<p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px;">
    If you're having trouble with the button above, you can also copy and paste this link into your browser:<br>
    <a href="{{surveyUrl}}" style="color: #2C5234;">{{surveyUrl}}</a>
</p>

<hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 20px 0;">

<p style="font-size: 12px; color: #666;">
    You received this email because you opted in to survey notifications from Summit Ridge HOA. 
    You can update your preferences at any time by visiting your <a href="{{preferencesUrl}}" style="color: #2C5234;">account settings</a>.
</p>